title: Dallas 10x10 Who's Who at the Oil Baron's Ball.avi
description:
Yes boys and girls: DALLAS is back, and now that the long dream is over, its even better than ever!

Clayton feels he's fighting a losing battle with Jock's ghost for Miss Ellie; Sue Ellen looks to make a movie about her life with J.R.; Wes makes his claim public at the Oil Baron's Ball.

First Aired: 11/21/1986

This episode features the final appearance by John Zaremba as Dr. Danvers, as Zaremba passed away a month after this episode aired.
